{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"60d4de35de","title":"目前我党方针是拉蒋抗战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a2319c899","index":0,"year":1941,"month":6,"day":12,"articleId":"60d4de35de"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"aebdb8026b","type":"paragraph","text":"目前我党方针是拉蒋抗战","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"60d4de35de"},{"id":"31c5003044","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年6月12日）朱，陈、罗，黎、罗：据报：我一一五D六八六R以及东进队一部曾于号日尚仁和庄一唐家林一带常师蒙旅进攻，又一部约三干敬日向陈庄某家城新三十六D”进攻，我许、鱼、彭等部约五千分向开城某山屋基一带赵师进攻等情。是否有此等事，请查复。目前我党方针在拉蒋抗战。我军应坚持觉中央“人不犯我，我不犯人，人若犯我，我必自卫”的原则。如有此种进攻行动，希即停止。并告彭、左，陈，刘”。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"60d4de35de"},{"id":"78d1210a58","type":"paragraph","text":"毛朱王叶","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"60d4de35de"},{"id":"c97ff983f3","type":"paragraph","text":"六月文口这是毛泽东和来德、王祥、叶剑英给未璃、陈光、罗荣粗、黎12]指新三十六师[3）指新三十六师14]指新三十六师许，指许世友。鱼，不知是指谨，疑原抄件有误。彭，指彭嘉庆。指彭德杯、左权，陈毅，刘少音。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"60d4de35de"}],"page":{"id":"d9babb6dec","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"60d4de35de","start":132,"end":132}}}},"__N_SSG":true}